===Etymology===
{{OE.}} [[lufu]] (''noun''), [[lufian]] (''verb''), from Germanic ''*lubo'', from Indo-European ''*leubh-''.

{{tennis}} As a ''zero'' score in tennis, “love” derives from French [[œuf|l’œuf]] (“the egg”).

